## WarehouseAPI.sellProduct() method

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript

    divisionName: string,
    cityName: string,
    productName: string,
    amt: string,
    price: string,
    all: boolean,
  ): void;
```

|  Parameter | Type | Description |

|  productName | string | Name of the product |
